Introduction

Na Kamden, also known Na Du Bin, is a Korean-American singer and rapper under FNC Entertainment. He is known for participating in survival shows "Wild Idol" and "Boys Planet" 2023.

He made his official debut as a member of the boy group AMPERS&ONE on November 15, 2023.
